channel.title: PU : Sign Up Now! MoparScape Member's, Form as One!
channel.description:
[b]PU : Sign Up[/b] [i]Hello and welcome. This is a project I've started and would like to finish, with you guys. It's occured to me that, we, on this forum, aren't really a team. If only we could work together, not be greedy and help each other, it would be a much better place. Therefor, I am giving you a chance to give 'teamwork' one last chance. To sign up, just use the layout below. <3 Layouts.[/i]
[code] [b]Why I wan't to join : [/b] [i][/i]
[b]Why I think this will benifit the community : [/b] [i][/i]
[b]Tutorials/Sources I have released : [/b] [i][/i][/code]
[i]Ok, so this is how it works. [u]If[/u] I accept you into the team, you will receive a PM which will contain the link to the official PU forum. From there, you can download the source, talk about PU and talk about other things. I will [u]not[/u] be inviting people to our forum based on their Java skills but instead their social skills. Their manors and respect for others.[/i]
[b]What is 'PU'[/b] [i]PU is a project I've decided to put together because I beleive that all of us so far are 'in it to win it', unwilling to give 'teamwork' a try. PU stands for - Project Unknown because a name has yet to be decided.[/i]
